  "body": "# Feature Issue\n\n### User Story\n\n- As a user joining a token-gated community\n- When I am selecting addresses for permissions\n- I want to see the highest permission role I can join\n- So that I can make a more informed decision about which addresses to share.\n\n### Additional requirements\n\nThere are 4 places that would show the user's highest permission role:\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Overview screen</th>\n      <th>Request to join screen</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><img src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/46027/a790ea09-4b17-45eb-bf83-b6d1a3f1717c\" width=\"375\" /></td>\n      <td><img src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/46027/7c23ac13-6554-4a74-b6ff-85b32d1596d0\" width=\"375\" /></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Address selection screen</th>\n      <th>All permissions drawer</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><img src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/46027/ca8a4aa3-805d-4056-92ee-7d35743afb3b\" width=\"375\" /></td>\n      <td><img src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/46027/0b1070fa-4895-471e-9a9e-0975d0295989\" width=\"375\" /></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n### Suggestions\n\n- The highest permission role should ideally come from status-go. Double-check if this is not already implemented there. We may consider returning this piece of data in the same endpoint (may not exist now on 2023-12-08) that returns the data with all addresses and relevant tokens (implemented as part of https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/issues/18126)\n\n#### Action Point\n\nAsk desktop team if this functionality (highest permission role should ideally come from status-go) has been implemented.\n\n### Resources\n\n- Figma https://www.figma.com/file/h9wo4GipgZURbqqr1vShFN/Communities-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=15331-289598&mode=design&t=AIWaz4wOOOzVbMok-0\n\n### Blocked by\n\n- #18126\n- status-go work, TODO add issue link once created.",
